description: The low noise Terk Amplified Indoor HDTV Low Profile Antenna amplifier allows you to receive more stations, and features Terk's patented selectable bypass to ensure the perfect signal level in any situation. For maximum convenience, the built-in TV/Video selector switch allows you to switch between great TV programming and your favorite video source at the touch of a button. Although it's a high-performance antenna the low-profile design fits most TV cabinets and rotates 360° freely for easy adjustment and placement. Compact, low-profile design fits into even the tightest spaces. Switch between local TV programming and a video source at the touch of a button. Includes antenna base, 2 tuned receiving elements, VHF/UHF band separator, AC adapter and owner's manual.
title: Terk Low-Profile Indoor Antenna TV5 (Discontinued by Manufacturer)
